msgstr "# triton.language.semantic.less_than"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Comparing_Ops/lt.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Comparing_Ops/lt.md:4
msgid ""
"简介：用于比较两个张量的元素, 与`<`等价。\n"
"函数原型：\n"
msgstr ""
"Introduction: Used to compare the elements of two tensors, equivalent to `<`.  \n"
"Function prototype:\n"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Comparing_Ops/lt.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.semantic.less_than(\n"
" input: tl.tensor,\n"
" other: tl.tensor,\n"
" builder: ir.builder\n"
") -> tl.tensor\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Comparing_Ops/lt.md:8
msgid "作为`tensor`的内置运算符使用, 如`x<y`。"
msgstr "Used as a built-in operator for `tensor`, such as `x<y`."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Comparing_Ops/lt.md:10
msgid "## 2. OP 规格"
msgstr "## 2. OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Comparing_Ops/lt.md:12
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Comparing_Ops/lt.md:14
msgid ""
"| 参数名 | 类型 | 说明 |\n"
"| :---: | :---: | :---: |\n"
"| `input` | `tensor` | 张量数据, 左操作数, 代表要进行比较的主数据 |\n"
"| `other`   | `tensor` | 张量数据, 右操作数, 与`input`逐元素进行比较 |\n"
"| `_builder` | - | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type | Description |\n"
"| :---: | :---: | :---: |\n"
"| `input` | `tensor` | Tensor data, left operand, representing the primary data to be compared |\n"
"| `other` | `tensor` | Tensor data, right operand, compared element-wise with `input` |\n"
"| `_builder` | - | Reserved parameter, external invocation not supported for now |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Comparing_Ops/lt.md:16
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"`tl.tensor`：同`input`的shape的张量\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"`tl.tensor`: A tensor with the same shape as `input`.\n"

